name: SVGViewElement
description: The SVGViewElement interface provides access to the properties of <view> elements, as well as methods to manipulate them.

members.name: SVGViewElement.viewTarget
members.description: An SVGStringList corresponding to the viewTarget attribute of the given <view> element. A list of DOMString values which contain the names listed in the viewTarget attribute. Each of the DOMString values can be associated with the corresponding element using the getElementById() method call.
